      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经把Idle→Gated和Gated→SignalCheck这两条线画好了。接下来SignalCheck之后的分支怎么处理？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle",
        "Gated",
        "SignalCheck"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "SignalCheck之后有两个入口：EntryBUY和EntrySELL。EntryBUY的条件是PLC逻辑关闭值等于遥测流关闭值，且当前没有SELL持仓。EntrySELL则是MQTT Broker关闭值小于边缘节点关闭值，且没有BUY持仓。",
